strings: <Cap><leader> discovers a new recipe for the alchemy pot!
<se_high>*: It's been a long time since we've had visitors here in this poor lonely land.
<se_high>*: It used to be so lively around these parts, but now no one ever comes by.
<se_high>*: It's all because of those cursed thorns at Castle Trodain to the north of here. What a terrible affair.
<se_low>*: I heard a rumour about a magic key at Castle Trodain, so I went looking for it. I couldn't believe my eyes...
<se_low>*: I don't mean to interfere in your business, but I wouldn't go there if I were you. You might end up getting cursed too!
<se_low>*: Sorry. Did I scare you? That wasn't my intention. It's just...
<se_low>*: Never mind. Why don't we forget about that and do some business?
